    <h2>Iron Maiden Modes</h2>

   
    <h5><b>Fear of the Dark</b></h5>
    <p>
        <li>Hit one of the 4 lit purple shots then rip a spinner. </li>
        <li>Do this 3 times then shoot up the middle for soul shard.</li>
        <i>
            Note - after hitting any purple shot, the right ramp purple shot will stay lit.
            Hit it before hitting a spinner to double the value of the spinner rip.
        </i>

    </p>
    
    <h5><b>Flight of Icarus</b></h5>
    <p>
        <li>Shoot alternating lit ramps (yellow) as many times as possible during the timer.</li>
        <li>Once you've earned 20M points the Soul Shard is qualified.</li>
        <li>Shoot the bullseye target to end the mode early and light the Soul Shard OR you "risk it" and play it out like normal.</li>
    </p>

    <h5><b>Rime of the Ancient Mariner</b></h5>
    <p>
        <li>Center shot is lit (to shoot down the albatross) and collect a hurry-up counting down from 1M.</li>
        <li>Shoot center shot to lock in this value and start a 2-ball multiball.</li>
        <li>Shoot either of the two shots on the left side of the playfield to move them by one shot towards the center for 20 seconds.</li>
        <li>Shoot the bullseye once the shots are centered to score the jackpot.</li>
        <li>Repeat the process for the right side of the playfield (including the drop targets) to qualify the Soul Shard.</li>
    </p>

    <h5><b>Hallowed Be Thy Name</b></h5>
    <p>
        <li>Shoot one of the 4 lit orange shots (3M).</li>
        <li>Shoot captive ball (5M).</li>
        <li>Shoot one of the remaining lit orange shots (3M).</li>
        <li>Shoot all three drop targets (10M).</li>
        <li>Shoot one of the remaining lit orange shots (3M).</li>
        <li>Shoot bullseye target for 10M + 1M per time remaining. (note - this lights the Soul Shard).</li>
    </p>

    <h5><b>Aces High</b></h5>
    <p>
        <li>Fighters - shoot any blue shots to defeat fighters. Hit four to advance.</li>
        <li>Bombers - Shoot either ramp to "lock on" a bomber then shoot the center bullseye target for a jackpot.</li>
        <li>Repeat the above for the other ramp.</li>
        <li>
            The Ace - Hit the strobing shot, then the center bullseye within 5 seconds for a major jackpot,
            its value boosted by how close you hit the bullseye
        </li>
    </p>

    <h5><i>Soul Shard</i></h5>
    <p>
        Complete any Eddie battle mode to light the bullseye target for 10 seconds to collect a Soul Shard.
        Worth a hurry-up starting at 20% of the points earned during the battle
        (x2 or x3 depending on the accuracy of the bullseye target hit).
    
    </p>
